{"Sid":0,"Did":107625,"Id":"288587","Title":"陳正雄","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/person/2020-02-24/007ce239-77c0-4aac-9bda-9748c7a0ede6/collection/fd43c48c-707f-4d62-8d92-e85b677fc334/108-lit-pn-265-201911172337465dd0c180c331a0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_People","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n陳正雄，宜蘭縣冬山鄉人，1943年生。筆名宜嵐、文雅、正文。曾任羅東林區管理處人事室主任、公路局第四區工程處人事主任。 在報章雜誌上發表短篇小說、小說、散文合計約一百多篇，作品曾獲台灣省新聞處散文徵文得獎、中華日報新人專欄小說徵文入選、林務局徵文得獎。收在《一帆斜月過楓橋》裡的小小說，短篇小說，散文都是曾在報章雜誌上發表的作品。陳正雄認為︰「文學描寫人生的目的是創造美好人生，啟示人生向上、向善。因此我期望能創作不是消極而是積極，能使人產生共鳴，變化氣質，鼓舞人們激發奮鬥力量的作品。」\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7537404","Keyword_Latitude":"24.631919","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/person/02CCDF87-6254-4F13-8F64-BA21EBB62600","Original_Identifier":"288587","Keyword_Subject_1":"人物與團體","alias":"宜嵐;文雅;正文","Keywords":"《一帆斜月過楓橋》 / 林務局 / 陳正雄","bornStr":"民國/戰後時期","deathStr":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 13:43:12","Creator":"黃憲作;王怡云","language":"","dataSource":"","timelines":"","bornPlace":"","bornAddress":"","bornCity":"宜蘭縣","deathPlace":"","deathAddress":"","deathCity":"","sameAs":"","onlineAuthLink":"","job":"","organization":"","expertise":"","worksFor":"","gender":"男","citizenship":"中華民國","bornLng":"121.7537404","bornLat":"24.631919","deathLng":"","deathLat":"","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","url":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/person/2020-02-24/007ce239-77c0-4aac-9bda-9748c7a0ede6/collectionOpen/815d17e1-8f82-4ca5-90c1-cd750c334976/108-lit-pn-265-re-201911172340415dd0c180c331a0.jpg"}}